  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A game like none other.  Victim invites you into the world of The Ominous Oppression.  A desolate landscape of horrors and mental anguish.  A place where only the mentally strong can survive and overcome the seemingly endless relentless trials of perpetuating devastation.   <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984240/extras/ffd47f1570e66096cdfcc5ddd7086a88.avif?t=1772679617\" width=548 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as the Vulnerable Victim has no idea who he is. Has not idea where he is. And has so many questions as to why he must endure so much pain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984240/extras/105f1f76bdfe9e610d40a66944b655d4.avif?t=1772679617\" width=548 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect hundreds of items and abilities towards instilling a sense of confidence and competence.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984240/extras/5ae42cc4073154afb9905f95b57598f2.avif?t=1772679617\" width=548 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive a world populated with many threats and hazards that beckon certain doom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore top-down environments merged with dangerous 2D platforming </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect items & power-ups</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new areas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve a large variety of puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find hidden secrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive all threats</p></li></ul>",
